_:N5c8a793d8f4b44a58a6680f4bfdb2fc1 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Janet Daby was the Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Children and Families) at the Department for Education between 9 July 2024 and 7 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the Labour MP for Lewisham East in June 2018.</p>\n\n" .
